                        <interp inst="t18450915-name-218" type="given" value="PARCEVAL"></interp>PARCEVAL PARKER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the employ of Mr. Benjamin Prew, at No. 295, Holborn-hill. On the 28th of Aug., a little after eight o'clock at night, I was standing inside the shop—I turned round to speak to a gentleman, and saw by the reflection of a glass something taken from the door—I turned round and missed a coat—I went a little way down the street, and met the officer with Clarke and the coat—I had seen it safe not two minutes before—this is it—this is the ticket that was on it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
